  "keyFeatures": [
    "Unified Python SDK with 30+ data providers (yfinance, FMP, Intrinio, FRED, etc.)",
    "Standardized data models across providers with OBBject return type",
    "FastAPI REST server (openbb-api) for workspace and app integrations",
    "MCP server (openbb-mcp) for AI agent tool access",
    "Interactive CLI for command-line financial data exploration",
    "Extensions for equity, crypto, derivatives, fixed income, economy, ETF, and more",
    "Built-in charting, quantitative analysis, and technical indicators",
    "OpenBB Workspace integration for enterprise dashboards and AI copilots"
  ],
